<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="depend-vi">depend <strong><em>vi</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'pend/    美 /dɪ'pend/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.****</h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="depend-on-upon">depend on / upon</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>依靠；依赖(rely on / upon)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>depend on</strong> energy <strong>to</strong> do many things in our daily lives.  
在日常生活中，我们做很多事都离不开能源。</p><footer>人教⑥ – 4</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If our parents do everything for us children, we won’t learn to depend on ourselves. 
如果父母替我们这些孩子做所有的事情，我们就学不会独立。</p><footer>2010 上海</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>depend on</strong> him <strong>finishing</strong> the job this weekend.
我们指望他这个周末能完成工作。</p></div>

<p>2.★ <strong>相信；信赖：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Depend upon it, we shall solve the problem at last.
请相信，我们最终会解决这个问题。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You can depend on Jane — she always keeps her promises. 
你可以信赖简，她总是信守诺言。</p></div>

<p>3.★ <strong>由…决定；取决于：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How much sleep you need depends a lot on your age.
你需要多少睡眠主要取决于你的年龄。</p><footer>2017 浙江</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The journey takes about two hours, depending on traffic.  
旅途大约需要两小时，这取决于交通状况。</p><footer>2011 上海</footer></div>

<h3 id="it-that-all-depends">It / That (all) depends.</h3>
<p>1.<strong>那得看情况。</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— How long are you staying?
你会待多久？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— I don’t know. It depends. 
我不知道，那得看情况。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>dependence /dɪ'pendəns/ n   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is his mother’s dependence. 
他是母亲的依靠。</p></div>

<h2 id="_4">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— What are you going to do this weekend?
— <strong><em>_</em></strong>. If time permits, I may go to Shanghai with my friends.   （2012 福建）<br />
A.Don’t mention it<br />
B.It doesn’t matter<br />
C.Forget it<br />
D.It depends  </li>
<li>Don’t always d<strong><em>_</em></strong>_ on others. You should learn to rely on yourself.  （2007 浙江）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. D  2. depend  </p></div>